original_title: 元地方局アナウンサー 人妻 徳島えり AV Debut！！
overview: "I wanted to shine as a woman again in front of the camera ..." Former announcer "Eri Tokushima" who was active in the XX station until 6 years ago is Madonna's exclusive AV debut! !! Her refreshing and neat face and elegant and humble behavior make her a 32-year-old wife who gets the impression that she is a'morning face'. She seemed to be on a smooth sail at the beginning of her marriage, but she missed those days when she was an announcer day by day ... The popular female announcer of the local station is all three of the shameful productions delivered to all the people! !!
title: Based On Local Station Announcer Married Tokushima Eri AV Debut! !
